name: Time Cemetery
description:
You are stuck in the time cemetery! Reality is slowly falling apart around you. Get to the time warp pumpkins to escape before your time runs out.

You have 10 seconds to complete each level. The faster you complete a level, the more time you will have on the next one. If you die, you return to the previous level and start with 10 seconds again.

Keep an eye out for friendly ghosts and green time orbs that will help you to escape.
